{"id":638708,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/03/【旧闻重温】内蒙古男子称新冠病毒是美国基因/","date":"2020-03-16T08:30:01Z","modified":"2020-03-16T08:30:16Z","title":"【旧闻重温】内蒙古男子称“新冠病毒是美国基因武器” 被行政拘留十日","content":"<p><strong>新闻发布时间：</strong>2020年2月9日   来源：观察者网</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/ETN4fDEUwAEcJON.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638709\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/ETN4fDEUwAEcJON.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"691\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/ETN4fDEUwAEcJON.jpeg 576w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/ETN4fDEUwAEcJON-195x300.jpeg 195w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>据2月8日的内蒙古新闻联播报道，通辽市科左后旗朝鲁吐镇居民满某1月26日在快手APP上发表名为“经典话题：不听的后悔一辈子”的短视频。</p>\n<p>他在视频中编造说：“现在的新型冠状病毒引起的肺炎，是美国向中国使用病毒基因武器造成的”。该视频在快手的播放量达到近一万四千次。</p>\n<p>苏继成律师接受采访时强调，在疫情防控期间，任何组织和个人不得制造和故意传播谣言，否则将可能处以十日以下拘留；构成犯罪的，将最高判处七年以下的有期徒刑。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/20200209115828961.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638710\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/20200209115828961.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"318\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/20200209115828961.jpg 795w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/20200209115828961-300x191.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/20200209115828961-768x489.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Some <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/influenza?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#influenza</a> deaths were actually infected with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/COVID?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#COVID</a>-19, Robert Redfield from US <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/CDC?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#CDC</a> admitted at the House of Representatives. US reported 34 million cases of influenza and 20,000 deaths. Please tell us how many are related to COVID-19? <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CDCDirector?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@CDCDirector</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/vYNZRFPWo3\">pic.twitter.com/vYNZRFPWo3</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Lijian Zhao 赵立坚 (@zlj517) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/zlj517/status/1238114622684585984?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 12, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">2/2 美国疾控中心主任被抓了个现行。零号病人是什么时候在美国出现的？有多少人被感染？医院的名字是什么？可能是美军把疫情带到了武汉。美国要透明！要公开数据！美国欠我们一个解释！ <a href=\"https://t.co/vYNZRFPWo3\">pic.twitter.com/vYNZRFPWo3</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Lijian Zhao 赵立坚 (@zlj517) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/zlj517/status/1238113459234934785?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 12, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"6AipDVxQye\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/03/%e7%be%8e%e5%9b%bd%e4%b9%8b%e9%9f%b3%ef%bd%9c%e4%b8%ad%e5%9b%bd%e5%8f%91%e8%a8%80%e4%ba%ba%e8%b5%b5%e7%ab%8b%e5%9d%9a%e7%a7%b0%e5%8f%af%e8%83%bd%e6%98%af%e7%be%8e%e5%86%9b%e5%b0%86%e7%96%ab%e6%83%85/\">美国之音｜中国发言人赵立坚称可能是美军将疫情带到了武汉</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《美国之音｜中国发言人赵立坚称可能是美军将疫情带到了武汉》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/03/%e7%be%8e%e5%9b%bd%e4%b9%8b%e9%9f%b3%ef%bd%9c%e4%b8%ad%e5%9b%bd%e5%8f%91%e8%a8%80%e4%ba%ba%e8%b5%b5%e7%ab%8b%e5%9d%9a%e7%a7%b0%e5%8f%af%e8%83%bd%e6%98%af%e7%be%8e%e5%86%9b%e5%b0%86%e7%96%ab%e6%83%85/embed/#?secret=6AipDVxQye\" data-secret=\"6AipDVxQye\" width=\"6